Had great taste, although sauce didn't thicken like it was supposed to. We really liked the rosemary & proscuitto combination. Was very easy to prepare; nice autumn dish.

Rating: 2
Nothing special. Too many good chicken recipes out there, I don't think I would make this again.

Rating: 4
This is a great company dish. Make it ahead and forget about it. I added some crushed red pepper to give it a little kick and an extra pack of chicken breasts (boneless/skinless). It went great with the poached pear recipe in the same article.

Rating: 2
I made this recipe as is, as I usually do with something the first time. The flavor was OK, but I guess I expected more, given the incredients. The sauce didn't thicken up as I had hoped.